{"tid":1110453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港人熱搜「黃心穎」　Google搜尋破20萬次揮低「巴黎聖母院」","createTime":"2019-04-16T14:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T05:03:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":45,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"bedb7024425724e5202ab0b37d7e1782585de640","tid":1110453,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"無綫女藝人黃心穎與已婚男歌手許志安被爆出軌，被在的士車廂內火熱激吻20次。長達16分鐘的影片曝光後數小時，「黃心穎」一詞在Google Trend累積搜尋突破20萬次，遠超震撼全球的巴黎聖母院大火。<br />\n<br />\n根據Google Trend資料，截至下午5時，「黃心穎」累積搜尋逾20萬次，相較排第二、逾5萬次搜尋的「巴黎聖母院」多出3倍，而深水埗槍擊案使用的「石屎槍」排第四。<br />\n<br />\n而今次出軌風波，連帶許志安太太「鄭秀文」、黃心穎男友「馬國明」等人在Google搜尋也水漲船高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/20/13/10201379_787079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F20%2F13%2F10201379_787079.jpg&h=029cee15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/04/16/010114570.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F04%2F16%2F010114570.shtml&d=gujWeq0O8VISlzAOvjwOFrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=0ea6cd5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/04/16/010114570.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"14f87ff1d3acb964742036646267c539205b370d","tid":1110453,"uid":135293,"like":217,"dislike":31,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"又借題發揮<br />\n係啦係啦 唔理心安就一定最高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b298391a2c37e15bfac727f64ccb8d036c8a65d","tid":1110453,"uid":28800,"like":301,"dislike":57,"score":244,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fef4443c5076952939d2de518cb2dca3ce06dca","tid":1110453,"uid":37136,"like":83,"dislike":20,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"聖母院十級地震，大審判都唔關港豬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"